import React from 'react' import styles from './InfoPage.module.css' import { selectItem } from '../State/itemSlice' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' function InfoPage({ setVisibleInfo, data }) { const item = useSelector(selectItem) const dataItem = data.filter((_, id) => id === item)[0] return (
setVisibleInfo(false)}>
{`${dataItem.userName}`}
{`${dataItem.typeRequest}`}
) } export default InfoPage
